title: Ikar Tosafot Yom Tov on Mishnah Keritot
enDesc: Ikar Tosafot Yom Tov is an abridged version of Rabbi Yom Tov Lippmann Heller’s (1579 - 1654) classic commentary on the Mishnah - Tosafot Yom Tov. The author’s objective for writing his commentary was to add to and complement the Bartenura.
